317
00:37:48,817 --> 00:37:50,317
Len tam na mňa počkaj.

318
00:37:53,817 --> 00:37:56,317
Pôjdem ti podať správu
skôr či neskôr.

319
00:38:07,817 --> 00:38:08,817
Hoci vtedy

320
00:38:09,317 --> 00:38:10,817
už zrejme budem starý pán.

321
00:38:11,817 --> 00:38:14,317
Možno ma ani nespoznáš.

322
00:38:45,817 --> 00:38:48,817
Divné, kde je obraz?

323
00:38:51,317 --> 00:38:52,317
Da Ye, Da Ye!

324
00:38:52,817 --> 00:38:53,317
Poď sem!

325
00:38:53,817 --> 00:38:55,317
Pozri, ten obraz odrazu zmizol!

326
00:38:55,817 --> 00:38:56,317
Ako to?

327
00:38:56,817 --> 00:38:58,317
Sú káble zle zapojené?

328
00:38:58,350 --> 00:38:59,800
Pamätám si, že si kúpila VCR;

329
00:38:59,817 --> 00:39:00,317
