351
00:40:20,817 --> 00:40:21,817
Je skvelé byť nažive.

352
00:40:24,817 --> 00:40:25,817
Ling.

353
00:40:28,817 --> 00:40:29,817
Pamätáš, keď sme

354
00:40:30,317 --> 00:40:31,317
